						               													<description>Caps And Stones is a fast paced 2 player abstract game that focuses on trying to think 5 moves ahead with an ever changing play area. Games normally take 5-15 minutes to play and it only takes about 30 seconds to learn. Once you get the hang of the basic rules of play, an advanced twist on the rules is available to incorporate into your gameplay for truly mind bending games!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Caps And Stones is a print and play game that only consists of 1 playing piece and you will need to print out about 30 pieces (3 sheets of paper). One person picks the pyramid side (Caps) and the other person picks the rubble side (Stones). Then players take turns drawing from the same pile, aligning, and stacking pieces until a player gets 4 of their side lined up in a square looking down on the play area. The first one to do that wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
